column1150:
22/Apr/24 15:51;jmurphy;From [~wshi] :

the Analytics returned no results could be as the victim of query failures in Snowflake side:
Around 8:20am, Martin Retail (4844)'s query failed in Snowflake side with the error "SQL execution internal error: Processing aborted due to error 300016:2841755390; incident 2877836.". We're contacting Snowflake support for the update for incident now (a similar issue happened on 2024-04-16 afternoon too...) we can continue to monitor on Looker/Analytics query executions, also, for Analytics users, please recommend to logout/login open sessions or "clear cache and refresh" once if needed. Thanks.;;;

