column1153:
04/Feb/24 09:50;jmeckert;[~jmeckert] [~jmurphy] [~cphuah] [~aobrien] [~MPeev] [~dredgate] [~zsribnick] [~jkuczmarski] 

Escalated to a P2; IMS PROD ICDExportDISH service not responding to requests; inventorynotificationrequests.  DISH unable to recieve updated addressable allocations from IMS for their INVIDI platform for several days.  Anymore delay would impact DISH linear addressable business; i.e., missed Yield Management System optimized allocation updates.

History of the the connectivity issue, error messaging can be found above. DISH Technical resource has been identified to assist where needed.;;;
